          "text": "\"On face value,” Mooney says, “this particular account of a sighting and the photographs submitted as proof amount to one of the most convincing cases for the species' survival that I have seen.” Many other ‘sightings' have been hoaxes, and many sincere seekers are victims of obsession.",
