          "text": "Though Pajama Sam is not an “educational game”, it is replete with the types of problems psychologists study when they examine thinking and learning.",
          "translation": "尽管睡衣山姆不是一款“教育游戏”，但它充满了心理学家在检查思维和学习时研究的问题类型。"
