          "text": "Of these, 25 were used to select the word for the first experiment, while the key issue – comparing verbal and non-verbal communication – was determined by only the 37 remaining subjects.",
          "translation": "其中 25 个被用来为第一个实验选择单词，而关键问题——比较言语和非言语交流——仅由剩下的 37 个受试者决定。"
