        {
          "text": "Hundreds of kilometres from major cities and many hours by road from the closest hospital or clinic, some rural Australians do not have easy access to doctors, nurses and dentists.",
          "translation": "一些澳大利亚农村人距离主要城市数百公里，距离最近的医院或诊所也有很多小时的车程，很难找到医生、护士和牙医。"
        },
        {
          "text": "Organisations such as the Royal Flying Doctor Service (RFDS) have been established to bring health services to outback Australian communities.",
          "translation": "皇家飞行医生服务中心 (RFDS) 等组织的成立旨在为澳大利亚内陆社区提供医疗服务。"
        },
        {
          "text": "The RFDS provides free medical care to people who live, work or travel in remote and regional parts of Australia.",
          "translation": "RFDS 为在澳大利亚偏远地区生活、工作或旅行的人们提供免费医疗服务。"
        },
        {
          "text": "This non-profit organisation is the oldest and largest airborne health service of its kind in the world, and since 1928 it has used small aircraft to send doctors and nurses to some of Australia's most far-away communities.",
          "translation": "这个非营利组织是世界上历史最悠久、规模最大的同类空中医疗服务机构，自 1928 年以来，它一直使用小型飞机将医生和护士送到澳大利亚一些最偏远的社区。"
        }
