        {
          "text": "We decided that the way to achieve this feeling of collaboration would be to concentrate on the process by which the work emerged during auditions and rehearsals.",
          "translation": "我们决定，实现这种合作感的方法是专注于试镜和排练期间作品出现的过程。"
        },
        {
          "text": "We chose a play that we felt allowed varied interpretations – Harold Pinter's The Lover, a modern one-act play with just two characters.",
          "translation": "我们选择了一部我们认为可以有多种诠释的戏剧——哈罗德·品特的《情人》，一部只有两个角色的现代独幕剧。"
        },
        {
          "text": "We decided we would use six actors cast as three different couples, and each pair would have a turn to perform on one of the three nights that the play was to be staged.",
          "translation": "我们决定使用六名演员扮演三对不同的情侣，每对演员将轮流在该剧上演的三个晚上中的一个晚上表演。"
        }
