        {
          "text": "One of them bore an inscription still partly legible after 3,800 years: \"Year 8 under his majesty the king of Upper and Lower Egypt...given life forever...of wonderful things of Punt.\"",
          "translation": "其中一个铭文在 3800 年后仍然部分清晰：“上埃及和下埃及国王陛下的第 8 年……被赋予了永远的生命……蓬特的奇妙事物。”"
        }
