          "text": "As we kept talking we realised that we could have a transformative effect on the future of New Zealand by highlighting the potential benefits of high-quality research.” The example Taylor gives is the $4.5 million gift to establish an information centre at the University's Marine Science laboratory on the coast at Leigh.",
          "translation": "当我们不断交谈时，我们意识到，通过强调高质量研究的潜在好处，我们可以对新西兰的未来产生变革性的影响。”泰勒举的例子是捐赠 450 万美元，用于在利海岸的大学海洋科学实验室建立一个信息中心。"
