          "text": "Adapted to life in the hot, desert inland, spinifex has developed tightly rolled leaves which reduce the effects of drought stress.",
          "translation": "为了适应炎热的内陆沙漠生活，三齿稃长出了紧密卷曲的叶子，可以减少干旱胁迫的影响。"
