          "text": "Once released, the chemicals then provide a barrier that inhibits the growth of any potential plant competitor near the thorn apple seedling.",
          "translation": "一旦释放，这些化学物质就会形成一道屏障，抑制刺苹果幼苗附近任何潜在植物竞争对手的生长。"
